Concertgoers who wanted a free ticket to the event (unless they were willing to pay for a VIP ticket) had to complete a series of tasks, or 'actions', such as volunteering, emailing a world leader, making a phone call, or otherwise meaningfully raising awareness of the goal: ending poverty.
