Since 2011, Global Citizen reports that more than 19 million supporter "actions" have been registered, targeting a wide variety of causes.
According to Global Citizen, these actions have helped world leaders commit and make policy proposals worth more than $37 billion that will change the lives of 2.25 billion people by 2030.
