In response to one of the most frequently asked questions on the Global Citizen website asking "Why do you think we can end extreme poverty?"
The group replied, "It's going to be a long and difficult road, and we're going to fall and fail at times.
But, like the civil rights and anti-apartheid movements before us, we will ultimately succeed because we are stronger together.
