After meeting at a nightclub, Ronaldo and Mayorga reportedly returned to the footballer's room, where he allegedly raped her anal, according to the complaint filed in Clark County District Court in Nevada.
Mayorga claims that Ronaldo fell to his knees after the alleged incident and that he told her that he was a "good guy" for "99 percent", but that he is sometimes left behind by "one percent".
The documents state that Ronaldo confirms that the couple had sex, but that it was with mutual consent.
Mayorga also claims that she went to the police and that photographs were taken of her injuries in a hospital, but that she later agreed to an out-of-court settlement because she was "afraid of the consequences" and because she was worried about the "public humiliation".
The 34-year-old now says she wants the arrangement annulled because she is permanently traumatized by the alleged incident.
